\begin_layout Subsection
Testing PHP
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
From Ubuntu 14.04 and later versions, 
\emph on
/var/www/html
\emph default
 is the specific directory that Apache uses to find and serves archives.
 In previous versions was 
\emph on
/var/www
\emph default
 As we want to try if the system is working fine, we have to change the
 owner of the directory
\emph on
 /var/www/
\emph default
 and its subdirectories because they belong to root user and we want to
 have permisions to make changes in them:
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard

\emph on
\begin_inset listings
inline false
status open

\begin_layout Plain Layout

$ sudo chown -R $USER:root /var/www
\end_layout

\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
After that, we are going to make a simple PHP file in 
\emph on
/var/www/html.
 
\emph default
First of all, we have to move into the directory:
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard

\emph on
\begin_inset listings
inline false
status open

\begin_layout Plain Layout

$ cd /var/www/html
\end_layout

\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
Then we type in the terminal
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard

\emph on
\begin_inset listings
inline false
status open

\begin_layout Plain Layout

$ gedit info.php
\end_layout

\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
If you don't have gedit installed you can use nano or vim in its place.
 When it is opened, you write the following content:
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard

\emph on
\begin_inset listings
lstparams "language=PHP"
inline false
status open

\begin_layout Plain Layout

<?php
\end_layout

\begin_layout Plain Layout

	phpinfo();
\end_layout

\begin_layout Plain Layout

?>
\end_layout

\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
Then save it and close the editor.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
Now, you have to open your favorite web browser and in the search bar write
 
\emph on
localhost/info.php
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
\begin_inset Float figure
placement H
wide false
sideways false
status collapsed

\begin_layout Plain Layout
\align center
\begin_inset Graphics
	filename im12_1.png
	lyxscale 70
	scale 70

\end_inset


\begin_inset Caption Standard

\begin_layout Plain Layout
